  "body": "<center>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 36px;\"><strong><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/2C8aEuq.png\" alt=\"mod id\" width=\"296\" height=\"298\" /></strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><em>Feel free to channel your anger, the Straw Dummy is indestructible!</em></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif;\">This mod requires Fabric API and Fabric Language Kotlin</span></strong></span>&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif;\">JOIN OUR DISCORD!</span></strong></span><br><a title=\"discord invite\" href=\"https://discord.com/invite/G4PjhEf\"><em><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://discordapp.com/api/guilds/707435077679841350/embed.png?style=banner2&amp;v=2\" width=\"337\" height=\"80\" /></em></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif;\">SUPPORT ME ON MY PATREON!</span></strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><a href=\"https://www.patreon.com/notsteven\"><span style=\"font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif;\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/5Wog2kV.png\" width=\"339\" height=\"69\" /></span></a></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif;\"><strong>NEED A SERVER?</strong></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><a href=\"https://bisecthosting.com/notsteven\"><span style=\"font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif;\"><img src=\"https://www.bisecthosting.com/partners/custom-banners/e4c02994-c687-4670-84d8-2bbbf94721e9.webp\" alt=\"bisect\" width=\"900\" height=\"142\" /></span></a></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 36px;\"><em><strong>What does it do?</strong></em></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">This mod adds a single thing: The Straw Dummy.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">It has infinite HP and Knockback Resistance, and will display the damage received by its side.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">You can place one by crafting the Straw Dummy item and right clicking on a block.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Right clicking with an item will place it on its body.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Shift right click will retrieve the Straw Dummy and it's equipments.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\n</center>",
